# Changelog for brand-migrate

## v2.0.0 - 2026-01-07
- **DEPRECATED**: 标记为废弃，请使用 `/lovstudio:rename-project` 代替
- 原因：交互太多，不够自动化

## v1.1.0 - 2025-12-25
- Auto-detect current brand from package.json, directory name, README
- Simplified to single argument: just provide new brand name

## v1.0.0 - 2025-12-25
- Initial release
- Interactive category-based confirmation system
- Support for multiple naming conventions (camelCase, snake_case, kebab-case, UPPER_CASE)
- Database migration script generation
- Dry-run mode for preview
- Git safety checks (clean working directory)
- Automatic file/directory renaming with git mv
- Post-migration checklist
- Optional commit generation

